      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Grizzly Glutton",
        "Client": "Master Angler of Kamura",
        "Description": "This is terrible... If it goes on\r\neating this much, there won\u0027t\r\nbe a single fish left for us to\r\ncatch! Hunt that thing before\r\nall the fish totally vanish from\r\nour rivers, will ya?",
        "Target": "Hunt an Arzuros",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Abus de poissons",
        "Client": "Ma\u00EEtre p\u00EAcheur de Kamura",
        "Description": "C\u0027est terrible. S\u0027il continue\r\n\u00E0 manger comme \u00E7a, il\r\nn\u0027y aura plus de poissons\r\n\u00E0 p\u00EAcher \u00E0 Kamura !\r\n\u00C9limine cette cr\u00E9ature\r\navant que les poissons\r\ndisparaissent, s\u0027il te pla\u00EEt !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Arzuros",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Golosone feroce",
        "Client": "Pescatore abile di Kamura",
        "Description": "\u00C8 terribile... Se continua a\r\nmangiare cos\u00EC, non ci rimarr\u00E0\r\npi\u00F9 un solo pesce da pescare!\r\nCaccia quel mostro prima che\r\nil pesce sparisca dai nostri\r\nfiumi, OK?",
        "Target": "Caccia un Arzuros",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Fieser Vielfra\u00DF",
        "Client": "Meisterangler von Kamura",
        "Description": "Schrecklich... Wenn das so\r\nweitergeht, gibt es f\u00FCr uns\r\nbald keinen einzigen Fisch\r\nmehr zu fangen! Jag den\r\nVielfra\u00DF, bevor alle hiesigen\r\nFische aus unseren Fl\u00FCssen\r\nverschwinden, ja?",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Arzuros.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Glot\u00F3n gris\u00E1ceo",
        "Client": "Maestro pescador de Kamura",
        "Description": "Qu\u00E9 desastre... Si sigue\r\ncomiendo as\u00ED, \u00A1no quedar\u00E1n\r\npeces para la gente de Kamura!\r\nCaza esa cosa antes de que\r\nvac\u00EDe nuestros r\u00EDos, \u00BFquieres?",
